rows.label: qst201805_msg0003
rows.name: Quick, let's go talk to them!

rows.label: qst201805_msg0004
rows.name:
Hey, hey, back up there.
If we go empty-handed, won't they just
tell us to get lost, like last time?

rows.label: qst201805_msg0005
rows.name:
Ah, you're right!
We need to get ready with gifts!

rows.label: qst201805_msg0006
rows.name:
...Okay then, we'll look for whatever
these Phonexes like.

rows.label: qst201805_msg0007
rows.name:
You can't get Pinfins around here,
so it'll have to be something else...
